Title: Cosderma Timeless skin Moisturizer
Description: Skin in need of intense moisture and repair for fine lines and wrinkles. Suitable for all skin types. Solution: Hyaluronic Acid AM Moisturizer is formulated to help draw moisture to your skin's surface and naturally fill in fine lines. Our unique high potency blend of Hyaluronic Acid and supporting extracts naturally restores the supple elasticity of healthy, youthful skin. Although the human body naturally contains hyaluronic acid with almost half of this being located in the collagen of the skin, as we age our hyaluronic acid levels decrease, so that by the time we reach our mid 40's we have roughly only half of what we require to maintain that youthful looking appearance. BUT....It's not all bad news! Scientific studies have shown that Hyaluronic Acid improves skin hydration, stimulates the production of collagen in skin and maintains skin elasticity. In fact, no other biological substance can retain as much water as Hyaluronic Acid, resulting in increased smoothness, softening and decreased wrinkles. It's like a cushion for your skin, hydrating & plumping out those dreaded fine lines and wrinkles! You can benefit from this Anti Aging dynamite by applying The Optimum Body's Hyaluronic Acid Serum twice daily, Powerful antioxidant properties neutralize free radicals to reverse damage caused by the sun, pollutants, and cigarette smoke, moisturizes your skin and promotes rapid cell growth, Quell dryness by helping skin retain its natural moisturizers

Description: Product Details - Cosderma HA + Vitamin C SerumCosderma Vitamin C 10% with Hyaluronic Acid Serum Helps reduce appearance of fine lines • Intense hydration, Fights Against Signs of Aging • Brightens complexion • 98% Natural. No parabens, sulfates, or phthalates ADVANCED HYALURONIC ACID SERUM from Cosderma has nourishing polysaccharides deriving from Cassia Angustifolia, an Indian plant. The polysaccharides in the ADVANCED HYALURONIC ACID SERUM bind with moisture on the skin to fill up fine lines, minimising the appearance of wrinkles. The wrinkle reducer helps skin feel and look smoother while protecting skin cells from advanced ageing. The ADVANCED VIT C WITH HYALURONIC ACID SERUM leaves skin feeling hydrated and youthful with a more even complexion. This serum is ideal for all skin types. Vitamin C Serum is the perfect solution for your anti-aging and wrinkle needs. Premium ingredients deliver potent results by nourishing and strengthening the skin, helping to diminish the appearance of fine lines, wrinkles, age spots, sun spots, and other skin pigmentation. How Does The ADVANCED HYALURONIC ACID SERUM Work? Hyaluronic Acid is made of polysaccharides that bond with moisture on and within the skin to help fill in and plump fine lines. The polysaccharides help to protect skin by creating a moisturising barrier to block free radicals. The serum is formulated with all-natural oils like Vitamin E and Organic Jojoba Oil to deeply nourish delicate skin. Key Ingredients That Make ADVANCED HYALURONIC ACID SERUM effective: Hyaluronic Acid (Plant Derived): Known as the "fountain of youth" compound, Hyaluronic Acid is a non-sulphated glycosaminoglycan distributed widely throughout connective, epithelial and neural tissues. It is one of the chief components of the extracellular matrix and contributes significantly to cell proliferation and migration. Hyaluronic Acid reduces the appearance of fine lines and wrinkles, strengthens collagen and elasticity, and promotes new skin growth.
